Package com.example.bettertrialbook.experiment

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfirmationFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    Ok pressed interface returning a tag corresponding to which confirmation it was for
    EditExperimentFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    Ok pressed interface returning the update description/region or to delete the experiment
    GeoWarningFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    Ok pressed interface to continue after geolocation required warning displayed
    TrialProfileFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    Ok pressed interface for either viewing profile or blacklisting user
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddTrialDialogFragment
    Fragment for adding a new trial to an experiment.
    ConfirmationFragment
    Fragment for user to confirm whatever "serious" action they are taking (ending/publishing/blacklisting etc)
    CustomTrialList
    A CustomList for displaying trials in an experiment view.
    EditExperimentFragment
    Fragment for editing experiment details like description or region
    ExperimentAddActivity
    Activity for adding new experiment.
    ExperimentViewActivity
    Activity for viewing experiment details.
    GeolocationActivity
    Handles the displaying of a map using Google Maps API Set up done using: Google Maps Platform, 2021-04-07, Apache 2.0, https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/android-sdk/current-place-tutorial
    GeoWarningFragment
    Fragment called when either: No username entered Username entered is already taken Title of fragment changes depending on which reason it was called for
    TrialProfileFragment
    Fragment for choosing an option after clicking on a trial/user.
